text: Patrick W. Browne was an American college football player and coach. He attended Spring Hill College, then played at Tulane University under coach Clark Shaughnessy,https://digitallibrary.tulane.edu/islandora/object/tulane%3A22945/datastream/PDF/view and then coached Spring Hill.https://archive.org/stream/corsair193209spri/corsair193209spri_djvu.txt He was assisted by Mike Donahue. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:American football ends Category:Spring Hill Badgers football coaches Category:Tulane Green Wave football players
